title: Census Mini Project
text:
library(tidycensus)
options(tigris_use_cache = TRUE)

dc_income <- get_acs(
  geography = "tract", 
  variables = "B19013_001",
  state = "DC", 
  year = 2020,
  geometry = TRUE
)
